reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 368/11: DESIGNATED HOUSING PROJECTS - SECTION 68 OF THE ACT
reg_info.reg_name_text: DESIGNATED HOUSING PROJECTS — SECTION 68 OF THE ACT
reg_info.citation: O. Reg. 368/11: DESIGNATED HOUSING PROJECTS - SECTION 68 OF THE ACT

content.content:
1. (1) For the purposes of subsection 68 (1) of the Act, a housing project set out in an item of a Schedule is designated for the transferred housing program referred to in that item.  O. Reg. 368/11, s. 1 (1). (2) For the purposes of subsection (1), the housing program referred to in an item is the housing program described in Schedule 1 to Ontario Regulation 367/11 (General) made under the Act for the program category number set out in the item.  O. Reg. 368/11, s. 1 (2). 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation).  O. Reg. 368/11, s. 2. Schedule 1   City of Brantford Item   Program   Housing Project

1. (1) For the purposes of subsection 68 (1) of the Act, a housing project set out in an item of a Schedule is designated for the transferred housing program referred to in that item.  O. Reg. 368/11, s. 1 (1).

2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation).  O. Reg. 368/11, s. 2.
